post.title: Hackaviz
post.contents:
<script>
import {Runtime} from "https://unpkg.com/@observablehq/notebook-runtime?module";

import notebook from "https://api.observablehq.com/d/e8186dc6a68b5179.js?key=65c8f0576a197717";

Runtime.load(notebook, (variable) => {
  if (variable.name === "tick") return {
    fulfilled: (value) => document.body.innerHTML = value
  };        
});
</script>
